No. 23,

Misc.

In re Disbarment of Alker. Francis E. Walter and William J. Woolston on the motion.

In view of the pendency of disbarment proceedings in the United States Court of Appeals and the United States District Court, the motion to vacate the order of disbarment (362 U. S. 985) and to reinstate the order of suspension (360 U. S. 908) is held until those matters are determined.
